Ranger Help for: harvest wood
===============================

SYNTAX:      harvest
USAGE:       forest,jungle
SLOT COST:   2
BASE SP:     10
SKILL TYPE:  creation

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to gather wood from the surrounding trees
for use in crafting. The wood can be used to carve bows, arrows,
torches, fish traps, and other useful items. The amount and quality
of wood gathered depends on the Ranger's skill level and the terrain.
Forests and jungles provide the best sources of usable wood.
